{"title":"农业中学短歌","authors":["贺羡泉"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":6,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业中学短歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贺羡泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农中小景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墙上挂着水车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屋角拴着水牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学生宿舍里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都放着闪光的锄头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风带着油菜花香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵阵扑进窗口；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"琅琅的读书声四处飘散，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴和着枝头鸟语啁啾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫下中农的子女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都有勤劳的双手；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下课钟刚刚敲响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就忙得热汗直流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一代新型农民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在农业中学里造就。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要问咱学校多大？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请看这辽阔的田畴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老犁手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧社会里当长工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从没进过校门口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今农中当教师，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"样样活儿都拿手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚穿草鞋手扬鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袖子卷到胳膊肘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把田间作课堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领着学生大步走。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗颗种子滴滴汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播进条条新犁沟；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要让公社新一代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都成祖国的好犁手！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁肩红心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子初进校门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹也担心，娘也担心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"担心个啥哩？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——爹娘都是庄稼人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼人的后一辈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咋能变成文弱书生："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩不能挑，手不能拎！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么建设咱新农村？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过了几个冬春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹也放心，娘也放心："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伢们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——手脚没变懒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皮肉没变嫩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真个能武又能文；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕风吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕雨淋；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百把斤担子一点不费劲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爹娘心欢喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逢人就谈论："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业中学就是好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教出来的学生呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个都有铁肩红心！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}